title: Oster Extra-Large French Door Air Fryer Countertop Oven, Stainless Steel, 60-Min Timer, 6 Cooking Functions, Versatile Accessories, Reduces Energy and Cooking Time
description: Elevate your culinary experience with the Oster Extra-Large French Door Air Fryer Countertop Oven. Its elegant French doors open with a single pull, facilitating easy access for removal and insertion of meals. Capable of fitting up to 15 x 12 baking pans, entire family-sized chickens, or two large pizzas, this oven effortlessly caters to your entire family's needs. Its six versatile cooking presets, including Bake, Toast, Broil, Warm, Air Fry, and Turbo Convection, provide immense flexibility for a plethora of dishes. With 99.5% less oil usage compared to traditional deep fryers, it promotes healthier eating without compromising on taste and texture.
